      "correct": 3,
      "justification_correct": "ISO 27701 PORG.1 (Privacy Notice) requires transparent communication of processing activities. This aligns with GDPR Article 13/14 transparency obligations and CCPA disclosure requirements.",
      "justification_wrong": "PROT addresses processing limits; PLOC addresses location; PCOL addresses authorization—none explicitly mandate transparent pre-collection communication."
    },
    {
      "num": 9,
      "text": "In privacy risk management, what is the primary purpose of conducting a Privacy Impact Assessment (PIA) before deploying a new data analytics system?",
