    {
      "num": 11,
      "text": "Under GDPR Article 35, a Data Protection Impact Assessment (DPIA) is mandatory when processing involves which of the following characteristics?",
      "tag": "Privacy Impact Assessments",
      "options": [
        "C. Collection of basic contact information for marketing purposes only",
        "D. Routine administrative data processing with minimal privacy risks",
