      "correct": 3,
      "justification_correct": "ISO 27701:2019 explicitly integrates Privacy by Design throughout its control objectives and implementation guidance. Section 6.2 emphasizes preventive controls embedding privacy into organizational processes before processing begins, aligning with GDPR Article 25.",
      "justification_wrong": "NIST Privacy Framework focuses on transparency and accountability rather than by-design principles. CCPA matrices target compliance gaps. PIPEDA Schedule 1 provides principles but lacks structured design integration equivalent to ISO 27701."
